text: Alexandra Mîrca (born 11 October 1993) is a Moldovan archer. Mîrca competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Alexandra Mîrca == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Moldovan archers Category:Olympians for Moldova Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău
